      <title>Seed systems, science and policy in East and Central Africa</title>
      <link>http://knowledge.cta.int/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Seed-systems-science-and-policy-in-East-and-Central-Africa</link>
      <description>
